{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/Crossfar_red-22_2.gif?t=1684087457\" /> <br><br>Master the art of zero gravity warfare in Crossfar! Fight as a pilot, lead as a captain, and conquer as a general in intense PVP battles to earn your wings. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/Crossfar_red-22_3.gif?t=1684087457\" /> <br><br>Perform spectacular maneuvers while free-floating and flying, as you zero down your aim to land your next shot center mass and reshape the frontlines of the galaxy! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/Crossfar_red-22_1.gif?t=1684087457\" /> <br><br>Prepare for tactical decision-making and explosive reactions at any moment! Work in a formation with your squad and utilize each drone's special abilities to gain supremacy over the battlefield. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/Crossfar_red-22_5.gif?t=1684087457\" /> <br><br>Disarm, disable, distract or destroy enemy pilots to sneak past and breach their gate. Lure your enemies into a trap to counter their offensive or keep them at bay with sheer firepower! It's up to you and your team how you address every situation!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/Crossfar_red-22_4.gif?t=1684087457\" /> <br><br>Grab your best squadron and join the competitive community in season tournaments, or watch the best professional teams battle it out in CROSSFAR LEAGUE!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1684087457","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/page.bg.jpg?t=16840